    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS system for exceptional throttle response across the power band. The chassis remains composed thanks to proactive rear subframe reinforcement and recently refreshed poly-bushings. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a functional factory variable M differential lock. While the exterior shows light patina consistent with a well-enjoyed driver\u2019s car, the compression numbers are healthy and the valvetrain remains quiet. A visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning purist.",
