    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of high-revving German engineering with this E92 M3. Powered by the legendary S65 4.0L V8, this unit features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a responsive M-Variable differential lock that ensures optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. This example is mechanically robust, with recent preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. While showing honest signs of use consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the hydraulic steering rack provides the tactile feedback modern EPS units lack. A true purist\u2019s spec ready for the canyons or the track.",
